Install pytest plugin:
    -pip install pytest-playwright

Install the required browsers:
    -playwright install

Run Test
    -pytest demo.py 

Run Test in headed mode:
    -pytest --headed demo.py 


Run Test and generate html reporter:
    -pytest --headed demo.py --html=report.html


Code Generator:  playwright codegen https://www.saucedemo.com/

Generate trace :
    -context.tracing.start(screenshots=True, snapshots=True, sources=True)
    -context.tracing.stop(path = "/Users/ganeshkafle/Playwright/trace.zip")


Trace viewer: playwright show-trace trace.zip